Portfolio Dashboard Design Specifications
1. Overview
This document outlines the design specifications for the responsive portfolio dashboard, including color schemes, typography, spacing guidelines, breakpoints, and component design decisions.
2. Color Palette
Primary Colors

Primary: #6366f1 (Indigo)
Primary Hover: #4f46e5 (Darker Indigo)
Secondary: #10b981 (Emerald Green)

Background Colors

Dark Background: #1e293b (Slate 800)
Card Background: #334155 (Slate 700)

Text Colors

Primary Text: #f8fafc (Slate 50)
Secondary Text: #cbd5e1 (Slate 300)
Muted Text: #94a3b8 (Slate 400)

Border Colors

Border: #475569 (Slate 600)

Status Colors

Success: #10b981 (Emerald Green)
Error/Negative: #ef4444 (Red)
Warning: #f59e0b (Amber)
Info: #3b82f6 (Blue)

Chart Colors

Chart Gradient Fill: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1) (Translucent Indigo)
Chart Line: #6366f1 (Indigo)
Doughnut Chart Segments:

#6366f1 (Indigo)
#8b5cf6 (Violet)
#a855f7 (Purple)
#d946ef (Fuchsia)
#ec4899 (Pink)
#10b981 (Emerald)



3. Typography
Font Family

System font stack:
cssfont-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, 
             Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Open Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;


Font Sizes

Extra Large (h1): 1.5rem (24px)
Large (h2): 1.25rem (20px)
Medium (h3): 1rem (16px)
Normal (body): 0.875rem (14px)
Small: 0.75rem (12px)

Font Weights

Regular: 400
Medium: 500
Semi-bold: 600
Bold: 700

4. Spacing System
The spacing system follows a consistent scale:

4xs: 0.25rem (4px)
3xs: 0.5rem (8px)
2xs: 0.75rem (12px)
xs: 1rem (16px)
sm: 1.25rem (20px)
md: 1.5rem (24px)
lg: 2rem (32px)
xl: 2.5rem (40px)
2xl: 3rem (48px)

5. Border Radius

Small: 0.25rem (4px)
Medium: 0.5rem (8px)
Large: 0.75rem (12px)
Circle/Pill: 9999px

6. Shadows

Card Shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 2px 4px -1px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06)
Dropdown Shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05)

7. Responsive Breakpoints

Mobile: < 768px
Tablet: 768px - 1024px
Desktop: > 1024px

Grid System Behavior

Desktop: Sidebar (240px) + Main Content (1fr)
Mobile: Full-width with collapsible sidebar

8. Component Specifications
Card Components
Stat Card

Padding: 1.25rem (20px)
Background: Card Background
Border Radius: Medium (8px)
Layout: Flex column with header row

Chart Card

Padding: 1.25rem (20px)
Background: Card Background
Border Radius: Medium (8px)
Chart Height: 250px

Navigation
Sidebar

Width: 240px
Background: Card Background
Item Padding: 0.75rem 1rem (12px 16px)
Item Spacing: 0.5rem (8px)
Active Item: Primary color background, White text
Hover Item: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1) background
Mobile Behavior: Off-canvas with overlay

Buttons and Inputs
Search Input

Height: 2.5rem (40px)
Padding: 0.75rem 1rem 0.75rem 2.5rem (12px 16px 12px 40px)
Border: 1px Border Color
Border Radius: Medium (8px)
Background: Card Background
Text Color: Primary Text

Chart Actions Button

Padding: 0.5rem (8px)
Border Radius: Small (4px)
Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1)
Active Background: Primary Color

9. Animation & Transitions

Default Transition: all 0.2s ease
Sidebar Transition: left 0.3s ease
Hover Effects: Subtle background/opacity changes

10. Chart Configuration
Line Chart (Portfolio Performance)

Line Tension: 0.4 (Smooth curves)
Fill: Subtle gradient
Grid: Hidden X grid, subtle Y grid
Tooltip: Currency formatting
Time Periods: Weekly, Monthly, Yearly

Doughnut Chart (Asset Allocation)

Cutout: 70%
Legend Position: Bottom
Legend Style: Circle point style
No Border: borderWidth: 0

11. Mobile Optimization
Mobile Navigation

Hamburger menu toggle
Off-canvas sidebar
Semi-transparent overlay
Touch-friendly tap targets (minimum 44x44px)

Mobile Content

Single column layout
Stacked cards
Reduced padding where appropriate
Header becomes column on small screens

12. Accessibility Guidelines

Color Contrast: All text meets WCAG 2.1 AA standard
Focus States: Visible focus indicators on interactive elements
Semantic HTML: Proper use of HTML5 semantic elements
Screen Reader Support: Appropriate ARIA labels where necessary
Touch Targets: Minimum size of 44x44px for mobile interactions

13. Icon System
Using inline SVG icons with the following properties:

Default Size: 18px or 20px
Stroke Width: 2px
Color: Inherited from text color
Alignment: Vertically centered with text

14. Data Visualization Best Practices

Color Differentiation: Distinct colors for different data categories
Interactive Tooltips: Detailed information on hover/touch
Responsive Resizing: Charts adapt to container width
Limited Data Points: Not overcrowding visualizations
Clear Labels: Readable typography and formatting


These design specifications serve as a comprehensive guide for maintaining design consistency across the responsive portfolio dashboard.
